    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 15 minutes 2-section demo of Ground Water - Episode of Dhanra: A platformer about squeezing and a quest to forge freedom. Follow Roshi's venture through the conflicts of Dhanra Village as a part of his journey to find a cure for the curse on his home. Navigate through winding paths and tactile environments that help express Roshi's potent squeeze and vessels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Piraiya and Squeeze</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ground-Water is set in a world inhabited by a sentient species known as the piraiya. With a peculiarly simple anatomy, their bodies are essentially vessels filled with water. They move primarily by sliding and perform all actions by squeezing their bodies to create and release tension within the water they contain.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.poster.avif?t=1760487310\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.webm?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.mp4?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roshi and His Vessels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roshi, the freedom-seeking protagonist, is a young piraiya discovering how altering the shape of his vessel can lead to diverse behaviors and interactions with the world around him.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/0214774a73d9aec49e739d20677cf63f.avif?t=1760487310\" width=232 height=496 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tall - Light on landing but a strong head bump. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/b5472131f9772fa85aab63ac11d96443.avif?t=1760487310\" width=342 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Square - Lands and jumps off like a champ. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/768a2eb418f6202eb60a6ddb9d32f989.avif?t=1760487310\" width=424 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wide - Lands to kill the ground. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactile Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roshi’s versatility is matched by the equally adaptable and tactile environmental elements that players can interact with in diverse ways. These elements are integrated into intricately designed areas with paths that branch, merge, and intertwine, allowing players to craft their own unique gameplay stories and moments.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.poster.avif?t=1760487310\" width=730 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.webm?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.mp4?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.poster.avif?t=1760487310\" width=780 height=1068 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.webm?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.mp4?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conflicts and Characters Of Dhanra</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This short gripping venture takes Roshi through Dhanra Village, a fabled stronghold of warriors and protectors of the valley. The village is home to colorful characters and enemies, each vibrant in their aesthetics, mechanics, and personalities. These characters drive a narrative that delves into how their capabilities and techniques spark conflicts, examining the interplay of duty, risk, control, and freedom that arises from these interactions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.poster.avif?t=1760487310\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.webm?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.mp4?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.poster.avif?t=1760487310\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.webm?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264550/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.mp4?t=1760487310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
